The paper discusses the technological advancements and evolutions for wireless communications beyond 5G networks, which falls under the category of network and internet architecture (cs.NI). The paper also discusses critical performance requirements, issues, enabling technologies, and challenges in designing 6G massive RANs, which can be categorized under information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper provides several artificial-intelligence-based approaches to overcome future challenges, which can be classified under artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
